   written in C, please refer to them.
   
   By default, they are located in
   
   /usr/local/natinst/nidaqmxbase/examples (Linux)
   
   or
   
   C:\Program Files\National Instruments\NI-DAQmx Base\Examples (Windows).
  ]]></EXAMPLE>

